# Project Structure

> **Apply Intelligently** - Project organization conventions.

## Overview

Wegoby projects live in `projects/` folder. Each is an independent repo with its own git.

**Important**: Projects are gitignored from meta layer—only README.md is committed.

## Projects Folder

```
projects/
├── README.md                    # Explains structure (committed)
├── percepta/                    # Adaptive UI engine (gitignored)
├── sensetree/                   # Empathic AI service (gitignored)
├── wegoby-portfolio/            # Main website (gitignored)
└── wegoby-server/               # Backend services (gitignored)
```

